Rules & Guidelines-

Can you please link the rules and tell us what you think is good or bad about them. https://www.nopixel.net/upload/index.php?threads/nopixel-official-rules-guidelines.104748/ I think they are good,straight foward and not too hardcore. I like how MetaGaming, PowerGaming and RDM are not allowed because on my previous experiences in RP was on ArmA 2 and there was none of this except sometimes rdm but people didn't really care because it wasn't whitelisted.
What is your definition of roleplay? To roleplay is the act of speaking and acting as someone else and live that character. Forget everything you know from real life and feel and live like your character.
What type of characters have you roleplayed before? I roleplayed civilians(Arma2,arma3), i tried police and EMS but only on Arma2, and criminal(arma2, 3).
What type of characters do you intend to roleplay? Italian descendence man born in Portugal but soon moved to Italy to work with is uncle, later finds what kind of business his uncle was running, he finds out he's uncle is a italian mafia's underboss. In the beginning he doesn't like the idea of living a life of crime but with his uncle by his side teaching everything he needed to know to survive in this underworld. Soon he starts to enjoy it and going fast up on the mafia ranks, he starts as a soldati, but once he reaches the capo not everyone is kin on this fast growth because for others wasnt so easy.
So after two years of being in the mafia your uncle is murdered and you are being framed of it because they say you are hungry for power and you wanted to take his place, but after you investigate you find out it was another capo who took advantage of the others jellousy however now its too late as the Don already started a manhunt after him. So he had no choice but to leave on the first flight which was to Los Santos without any belogings because the mafia was already scouting the house and everything in his name.
What are your character positives and negative characteristics?
Positive: Very hard worker
		  Loyal
		  Honest
		  Ambitious
		  Determined
		  Experienced in organized crime
Negative: Materialistic
		  Stubborn
		  Greedy
When do you feel is a good time to break character? Never. Always play out the situation and deal with it later on the forum or discord.
